Admin Functions
User Management

View, edit, and delete user accounts.
Reset passwords or manage account recovery requests.
Assign user roles and permissions.
Academic Management

Create and manage assignments.
Schedule and update exam timetables.
Track students' academic progress and analytics.
Content Moderation

Approve or reject user-generated content (e.g., forum posts, social network discussions).
Manage club and organization listings.
Monitor and remove inappropriate content.
Event Management

Create, edit, and delete events, workshops, and seminars.
Track RSVPs and attendance statistics.
Publish volunteer opportunities and manage submissions.
Health and Wellness Resources

Upload and manage mental and physical health resources.
Schedule wellness events or workshops.
Financial Oversight

Manage and update fee structures.
Approve or reject scholarship applications.
Provide financial literacy resources and track user engagement.
Career Services

Publish internship and job opportunities.
Approve or edit career-related resources and events.
Assign and manage mentorship opportunities.
Communication and Support

Chat with users in real-time to resolve complaints or queries.
Send broadcast notifications to users (e.g., reminders, announcements).
Analytics Dashboard

View platform-wide analytics, including user engagement, academic performance summaries, and financial reports.
Generate reports on student progress and app usage trends.
